Question: The left and right image contains the same number of black container of lotion with one lid sitting vertical.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://lululovelash.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/once-upon-a-time3.png?w=300&h=300

Right image URL: https://ifiwerequeenoftheworld.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/img_1100.png

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many black container of lotion with one lid sitting vertical are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many black container of lotion with one lid sitting vertical are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
